BT 1 0 0 1 30 372.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 363.6756 Tm (      3.2 Equipment Analysis) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 355.2756 Tm (      Calibration station EQ-CAL-001 was inspected on 2022-09-12. The optical sensor showed measurable degradation in) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 346.8756 Tm (      sensitivity, causing a systematic positive bias in fluorescence readings. S2 signal was unaffected because the S2) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 338.4756 Tm (      channel uses a separate optical path. Sensor was replaced during emergency PM \(WO-2022-0310\) on 2022-09-14.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 330.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 321.6756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 313.2756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 304.8756 Tm (      3.3 Material Review) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 296.4756 Tm (      All sensor cartridge lots and reagent cards used during the affected period were reviewed. No material changes were) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 288.0756 Tm (      identified. The same CART lot \(CART-2022-04-001\) was used throughout, ruling out material variation as a contributing) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 279.6756 Tm (      factor.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 271.2756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 262.8756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 254.4756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 246.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 237.6756 Tm (      4. Root Cause Analysis) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 229.2756 Tm (      Root Cause: Equipment aging - gradual degradation of the optical sensor on calibration station EQ-CAL-001 \(S1) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 220.8756 Tm (      channel\).) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 212.4756 Tm (      5M Category: Machine \(Milieu/Equipment\)) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 204.0756 Tm (      Contributing Factors:) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 195.6756 Tm (      - PM interval of 6 months was too long for the optical sensor component.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 187.2756 Tm (      - SPC monitoring detected the trend, but alert threshold was set at specification limits rather than at a tighter warning) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 178.8756 Tm (      level.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 170.4756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 162.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 153.6756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 145.2756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 136.8756 Tm (      5. Conclusions and Corrective Actions) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 128.4756 Tm (      Conclusion: The calibration drift was caused by optical sensor degradation on EQ-CAL-001. No product was) Tj T* ET
